<h3 class="date"><a href="/2006/apr/07/">&#x27a0;</a> April 7, 2006</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    <div class="flickrentry entry">
        <h4>ESPN Baseball Gamecast</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/124931993/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="ESPN Baseball Gamecast" src="http://farm1.static.flickr.com/42/124931993_3a3390ae51_m.jpg" height="151" width="240" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>This flash app on <a href="sports.espn.go.com/mlb/scoreboard">ESPN's MLB site</a> is simply lovely.  Just enough information to follow the game, with handy infographics showing the pitches and plays.</p>

<p>I'm currently watching stuff recorded on my TiVo with my laptop next to me, displaying the gamecast.  When I see something exciting's happening, I can drop to live TV and watch the game.  Hooray for technology.</p>
        </p>

